      <li><strong>Tank weld coordination.</strong> We work with stainless welders for repair-weld decisions; honest math on weld vs replace.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 and EPA 608 Universal certified (#1346255700410).</strong> See our <a href="/credentials/licensed/">licensing page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>$120 commercial diagnostic, no after-hours surcharge.</strong> Phones answered 24/7.</li>
